        "icon": "📖",
        "title": "Surah Al-Fatihah (The Opening)",
        "body": "\n                    <p>The most important surah, recited in every rak'ah of prayer.</p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">بِسْمِ اللّٰهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيمِ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Bismillahir Rahmanir Rahim</div>\n                    <p>In the name of Allah, the Most Gracious, the Most Merciful.</p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">ٱلْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ ٱلْعَالَمِينَ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Alhamdu lillahi Rabbil 'aalameen</div>\n                    <p>All praise is due to Allah, Lord of all the worlds.</p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Ar-Rahmanir-Rahim</div>\n                    <p>The Most Gracious, the Most Merciful.</p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">مَالِكِ يَوْمِ ٱلدِّينِ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Maliki yawmid-deen</div>\n                    <p>Master of the Day of Judgment.</p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">إِيَّاكَ نَعْبُدُ وَإِيَّاكَ نَسْتَعِينُ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Iyyaka na'budu wa iyyaka nasta'een</div>\n                    <p>You alone we worship, and You alone we ask for help.</p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">ٱهْدِنَا ٱلصِّرَاطَ ٱلْمُسْتَقِيمَ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Ihdinas-siratal-mustaqeem</div>\n                    <p>Guide us on the Straight Path.</p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">صِرَاطَ ٱلَّذِينَ أَنْعَمْتَ عَلَيْهِمْ غَيْرِ ٱلْمَغْضُوبِ عَلَيْهِمْ وَلَا ٱلضَّآلِّينَ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Siratal-ladhina an'amta 'alayhim, ghayril-maghdubi 'alayhim wa lad-dalleen</div>\n                    <p>The path of those You have blessed, not of those who earned anger, nor of those who went astray.</p>\n                ",
