        "body": "\n                    <h4>Greeting Others</h4>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">السَّلَامُ عَلَيْكُمْ وَرَحْمَةُ اللَّهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهُ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Assalamu Alaikum wa Rahmatullahi wa Barakatuh</div>\n                    <p>\"Peace, mercy, and blessings of Allah be upon you.\"</p>\n                    <h4>Replying</h4>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">وَعَلَيْكُمُ السَّلَامُ وَرَحْمَةُ اللَّهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهُ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Wa Alaikumus-Salam wa Rahmatullahi wa Barakatuh</div>\n                    <h4>When Sneezing</h4>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Alhamdulillah — Others reply:</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">يَرْحَمُكَ اللَّهُ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Yarhamukallah — \"May Allah have mercy on you\"</div>\n                    <p>Response:</p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">يَهْدِيكُمُ اللَّهُ وَيُصْلِحُ بَالَكُمْ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Yahdikumullahu wa yuslihu balakum — \"May Allah guide you\"</div>\n                    <h4>Upon Seeing Something Nice</h4>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">مَا شَاءَ اللَّهُ لَا قُوَّةَ إِلَّا بِاللَّهِ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Ma sha Allah, la quwwata illa billah</div>\n                    <h4>When Beginning Something</h4>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Bismillahir-Rahmanir-Rahim</div>\n                    <h4>When a Calamity Befalls</h4>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">إِنَّا لِلَّهِ وَإِنَّا إِلَيْهِ رَاجِعُونَ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Inna lillahi wa inna ilayhi raji'un — \"Indeed we belong to Allah, and to Him we return\"</div>\n                ",
